{"tid":1630441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有無人見到有直升機","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:33:51.000Z","uid":54113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"423679057f38c588cc526b8de909b44f16d52de0","tid":1630441,"uid":54113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:31:33.000Z","msg":"落大雨 撒唔到粉？"},{"pid":"af301e051cce3c8aa685ecd5af912eddefa644b0","tid":1630441,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"678723f588e626a1a5fb9dfab5cfcdb9182ca71c","tid":1630441,"uid":228116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"係土瓜灣見到，係空中停左大約5分鐘，好近民居，清楚聽到佢隻翼旋轉既聲"},{"pid":"01fd373cb2bdc449e14ec954cdc4afc964a58e2c","tid":1630441,"uid":219006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"家維邨一帶聽到聲"},{"pid":"d3424af0b4e28a9d7475b631fa226c3a19831c7e","tid":1630441,"uid":305362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"黃埔有"},{"pid":"0628c28b5f9d671c0d9f7de16bd1b946c8e311bb","tid":1630441,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:27:42.000Z","msg":"而家係旺角上容盤旋緊，好撚嘈"},{"pid":"6fd5fa0c0c06c91142b500de0f7bcc67fd948898","tid":1630441,"uid":192168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0628c28b5f9d671c0d9f7de16bd1b946c8e311bb","tid":1630441,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:27:42.000Z","msg":"而家係旺角上容盤旋緊，好撚嘈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:29:40.000Z","msg":"我都見到"},{"pid":"2f6bc98ec9812c175b67205a22f1ae6064195783","tid":1630441,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:30:38.000Z","msg":"宜家何文田都聽到"},{"pid":"bdc6b4ece78f42a66a6452d3ec19bcc0e3b8d647","tid":1630441,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:30:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n